WEBVTT

00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:03.136
did I have a brain tumor,
did I have a problem with my heart,

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:05.736
one of the doctors said to me,

00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:10.976
"I have diagnosed you
with civilization's disease: burnout.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:14.360
And there's nothing
the medical profession can do for you.

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:17.080
You have to change your life."

00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:19.896
AG: Preventing work
from overtaking your life

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.936
seems harder than ever.

00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:24.240
But it might actually
be easier than you think.

00:01:25.080 --> 00:01:29.640
(Music)